The '''Quetzal Sisters''' were a squad of [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] femmes fatales used for covert missions. Under the command of [[General/Legends|General]] [[Orma Hundeen]], they were composed of [[Zeela Nall]], [[Nuri Pravada]], and [[Sheyne Tyndos]]. [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa]] once worked with them on [[Elerion]].

